	"subclassFeature": [
		{
			"name": "Circle of the Dragon",
			"source": "DrdCrcDrg",
			"page": 2,
			"className": "Druid",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Dragon",
			"subclassSource": "DrdCrcDrg",
			"level": 2,
			"entries": [
				"龙之圈的德鲁伊致力于所有龙的自然平衡，善与恶。有些人崇拜诸如{@deity Bahamut|Dawn War|DMG}或{@deity Tiamat|Dawn War|DMG}的生命，以寻求获得神圣的升华和龙的力量。无论他们的动机是什么，这些德鲁伊都带着炽热的激情和非凡的自豪感。",
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Emissary of the Dragon|Druid|PHB|Dragon|DrdCrcDrg|2"
				},
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Circle Forms|Druid|PHB|Dragon|DrdCrcDrg|2"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Circle Forms",
			"source": "DrdCrcDrg",
			"page": 2,
			"className": "Druid",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Dragon",
			"subclassSource": "DrdCrcDrg",
			"level": 2,
			"header": 1,
			"entries": [
				"你的圈子的仪式赋予你变身为所有领域中最可怕的生物的能力。从2级开始，你可以使用你的野性之形变身为{@filter a dragon with a challenge rating as high as 1|bestiary|challenge rating=[;&1]|type=dragon}，无视野兽之形表中的Max. 忽略野兽形状表的最大CR列。这包括你以前没见过的龙。此外，你可以变身为具有野兽形状表限制一栏中的移动速度的龙，但在你达到表上所示的相应德鲁伊等级之前，你不能使用这些移动速度。",
				"从6级开始，你可以变身为一条龙，挑战等级与你的德鲁伊等级除以3一样高，向下取整。",
				"{@filter Official Dragons by Challenge Rating (up to CR 6).|bestiary|challenge rating=[;&6]|type=dragon}"
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Emissary of the Dragon",
			"source": "DrdCrcDrg",
			"page": 2,
			"className": "Druid",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Dragon",
			"subclassSource": "DrdCrcDrg",
			"level": 2,
			"header": 1,
			"entries": [
				"二级时，你学会了说、读、写（%0%），当你进行与龙有关的智力或智慧检查时，你可以将你的熟练度加倍。此外，你对被{@condition charmed}或{@condition frightened}的救赎行为有优势。"
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Dragon's Breath Evolution",
			"source": "DrdCrcDrg",
			"page": 2,
			"className": "Druid",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Dragon",
			"subclassSource": "DrdCrcDrg",
			"level": 6,
			"header": 1,
			"entries": [
				"从6级开始，当你使用你的野性之形变身为一个没有呼吸武器的生物时，你可以在它的状态块中增加一个呼吸武器。这个呼吸武器必须来自于你能够变身的龙的属性块，例如（%0%）。"
			]
		},
